name: KryptoPunk/z 00
description:
Wrapped in candy coated pixels packages, we rip off that box and smash it into pieces. We came to put that punk in the punks. Appropriation and devastation. We raise this scream for pure, visceral, blasting creativity! We bring you the KryptoPunk/z from the wreckages of the Internet filthiest rooms and untold stories.

This is another step in our collaboration with Domenico Barra!
We can't sleep. Time is too urgent. Need to create is driving us mad. The outflow of glitch Revolta! Embrace it.

Format mp.4 1080x1080 Codec H.264
